OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fcloudy and overcast through the
OL,7,Fevening and overnight with outbreaks
OL,8,Fof light and patchy rain for all areas
OL,9,Fbut especially Argyll. Winds falling
OL,10,Flight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FAnother cloudy and dull day
OL,13,Fwith outbreaks of rain and drizzle
OL,14,Fthroughout, which may be heavy and
OL,15,Fpersistent at times, particularly over
OL,16,FArgyll. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
