OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fand breezy on Monday and Tuesday with
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain spreading east,
OL,8,Fperhaps becoming heavy and persistent
OL,9,Fat times. Drier with brighter spells
OL,10,Fon Wednesday.
